videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield swoops over the middle for a steal, lobs an oop to Katie Lou Samuelson, who taps it back in mid-air for a Dangerfield score.

tracking.trackingName: WCBB_One-Play (Samuelson taps savvy pass to Dangerfield for lay-in) 2019/2/6

videos.headline: Samuelson taps savvy pass to Dangerfield for lay-in

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson gets it done on both ends by swatting Lashonda Monk's shot, then runs the floor and lays in a zipped pass from Crystal Dangerfield.

tracking.trackingName: WCBB_One-Play (Samuelson swats shot, lays in dime from Dangerfield) 2019/2/6

videos.headline: Samuelson swats shot, lays in dime from Dangerfield
